{"tid":1965543,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[明星講一句好過安倍講一百句］旅居吉隆坡GACKT：日本癲嘅 唔夠危機感","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T08:15:15.000Z","uid":221265,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5d95e14de02e539139279e479de0ec0033e5e7","tid":1965543,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/215426_61b329657ed55ef1f8cb0b159dfba8c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F215426_61b329657ed55ef1f8cb0b159dfba8c7.png&h=e3e60e98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/215428_f21481d7812a836514271527d549bd8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F215428_f21481d7812a836514271527d549bd8f.png&h=398a8947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚上「真相坂上」特備節目越洋直播<br />\n吉隆坡都lockdown <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/miyukimi1208/status/1248226512538501121?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmiyukimi1208%2Fstatus%2F1248226512538501121%3Fs%3D21&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=237e7079\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmiyukimi1208%2Fstatus%2F1248226512538501121%3Fs%3D21&h=fe366b33\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/miyukimi1208/status/1248226512538501121?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nGackt好波<br />\n直言唔兜圈<br />\n直接話日本瘋狂 唔夠危機感<br />\n又話醫療崩潰 你會失去重要嘅人<br />\n比起（關心政府）賠償 自己條命緊要啲<br />\n如果因為自己關係（周圍去） 重要嘅人冇咗咁點？<br />\n大家明唔明！<br />\n<br />\n個節目即上trends1<br />\n<br />\n4月3日yoshiki都直言日本應盡快宣布緊急狀態<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/220315_fd09e6736eed4893b6e8d6d5beefe6a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F220315_fd09e6736eed4893b6e8d6d5beefe6a0.png&h=99e740ad